title: Tiger_for_x86pc_(by_Viper).iso
description:
English
=======

This is one already pacthed and ready to burn DVD image with Mac OS X Tiger 10.4.1 for x86 PCs based on this instructions: http://www.win2osx.net/forum/showthread.php?t=1046

It includes a SSE3 to SSE2 patch and others hacks. Thanks to all responsible for that!

Viper
